<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Test Bill Reminder</h1>
    
    <p>Hello <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

    <p>This is a test email to confirm your bill reminder settings are working correctly.</p>

    <p>Your current reminder settings:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Reminder days: <%= @reminder_preference.remind_days.join(", ") %> days before due date</li>
      <li>Overdue notifications: <%= @reminder_preference.send_overdue_reminders? ? "Enabled" : "Disabled" %></li>
      <li>Email frequency: <%= @reminder_preference.digest_frequency.titleize %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you received this email, your bill reminder notifications are properly configured.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Maybe Team</p>
  </body>
</html> 